{"tid":2070294,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"印度考慮 ban 52 款中國相關 Apps, 包括 Tiktok","createTime":"2020-06-19T04:37:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-20T18:32:25.000Z","uid":30647,"like":378,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":73,"replies":[{"pid":"f760dabfcff1f16a73000b9752b41e0d852ba193","tid":2070294,"uid":30647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T04:37:19.000Z","msg":"<strong>Intel agencies red-flag use of 52 mobile apps with links to China: Complete list</strong><br />\n<br />\nIndian intelligence agencies have asked the government to block or advise people to stop use of 52 mobile applications linked to China over concerns that these weren&rsquo;t safe and ended up extracting a large amount of data outside India, people familiar with the development told Hindustan Times.<br />\n<br />\nThe list of applications sent by the security establishment to the government include video conferencing app Zoom, short-video app TikTok, and other utility and content apps such as UC browser, Xender, SHAREit and Clean-master.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hindustantimes.com/india-news/intel-agencies-red-flag-use-of-52-mobile-apps-with-links-to-china-complete-list/story-B50Slf39aSnVOrCcS92l1N.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fintel-agencies-red-flag-use-of-52-mobile-apps-with-links-to-china-complete-list%2Fstory-B50Slf39aSnVOrCcS92l1N.html&d=OzCpETo5oS2N7QoMCn84CyZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=b6bf0954\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hindustantimes.com/india-news/intel-agencies-red-flag-use-of-52-mobile-apps-with-links-to-china-complete-list/story-B50Slf39aSnVOrCcS92l1N.html</a>"},{"pid":"4822be4a94976ba08ee45a867640ae00c3997601","tid":2070294,"uid":30647,"like":114,"dislike":1,"score":113,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T04:38:01.000Z","msg":"52個 Apps 名單<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N4a2tfr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN4a2tfr.jpg&h=e503